WEBVTT

00:01:57.692 --> 00:02:00.058
are frustrated.

00:02:00.058 --> 00:02:02.509
At BCG, we looked at this,

00:02:02.509 --> 00:02:04.340
and we asked ourselves,

00:02:04.340 --> 00:02:07.852
this can't be the right way of managing healthcare.

00:02:07.852 --> 00:02:11.072
And so we took a step back and we said,

00:02:11.072 --> 00:02:13.744
"What is it that we are trying to achieve?"

00:02:13.744 --> 00:02:15.975
Ultimately, in the healthcare system,

00:02:15.975 --> 00:02:19.936
we're aiming at improving health for the patients,

00:02:19.936 --> 00:02:22.213
and we need to do so at a limited,

00:02:22.213 --> 00:02:24.070
or affordable, cost.

00:02:24.070 --> 00:02:26.793
We call this value-based healthcare.

